      "name": "Curse of the Riddle",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Inteligência: CD 15, uma criatura the sphinx can see within 18 m. 21 (6d6) dano psíquico, and o alvo is cursed with a riddle. The cursed target has Desvantagem on ability checks and attack rolls. In addition, if it takes the Magic action, it must succeed on a CD 15 Inteligência saving throw or that action is wasted. The cursed target can take a Study action to make a CD 15 Inteligência check, solving the riddle and ending the curse on a success. The curse ends early if the sphinx curses another target.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
